From 0000000000000000000000000000000000000000 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: minekube <opensource@minekube.com>
Date: Sat, 2 May 2026 00:00:00 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] Register :geyserlite-native subproject

Adds the overlay subproject to settings.gradle.kts so the GraalVM
native-image build can produce libgeyserlite.so alongside the
standard standalone artifact.

The subproject lives in geyserlite-native/ at the repo root, added
by build/apply-overlay.sh before this patch is applied.
---
 settings.gradle.kts | 3 +++
 1 file changed, 3 insertions(+)

diff --git a/settings.gradle.kts b/settings.gradle.kts
index 0000000..0000000 100644
--- a/settings.gradle.kts
+++ b/settings.gradle.kts
@@ -28,3 +28,6 @@ include(":velocity")
 include(":viaproxy")
 include(":common")
 include(":core")
+
+// geyserlite overlay (added by https://github.com/minekube/geyserlite)
+include(":geyserlite-native")
